**STATUS:** PARTIALLY SOLVED

**Part 1 (SOLVED):** f(n) = o(2^n)
- Verstraëte (2004): f(n) ≪ 2^{n - n^{1/10}}
- Nenadov (2025): f(n) ≪ 2^{n - n^{1/2-o(1)}}

**Part 2 (OPEN):** Does f(n)/2^{n/2} → ∞?

**Limit (OPEN):** Does lim f(n)^{1/n} exist?

**Current Gap:** 2^{n/2} < f(n) ≪ 2^{n - √n}
